text.tspan: Dating is hard. Dating is really hard.
First you have to find someone with
whom you share a mutual attraction…
Taylor Bolduc – On 20th February, 2015 – Web Culture
It seems most everyone has a fitness
tracker these days, and most of them
have a very utilitarian, sporty look.
Most of us were thrown for a loop when
responsive design came into being. We
tried to jam it into our existing, pixel…
